Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.25,0:00:11.12,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是矩阵其实没那么无聊，甚至很有意思
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.25,0:00:11.12,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}However, matrices are not so dull and can be very interesting.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.82,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个视频就让我们来揭秘矩阵的三重身份
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.82,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In this video, let's unveil the three roles of matrices.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.80,0:00:23.52,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}矩阵，它既是数据仓库，可以帮你存储信息
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.80,0:00:23.52,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A matrix is a data repository that helps store information.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:23.77,0:00:27.75,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它又是空间建筑师，可以用来构建高维空间
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.77,0:00:27.75,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It is also a spatial architect that can construct higher-dimensional spaces.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.02,0:00:31.75,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它还是魔法师，能施展线性变换的魔法
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.02,0:00:31.75,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And it is a wizard capable of performing linear transformation magic.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.97,0:00:35.82,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先来看它的第一个身份,数据仓库
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.97,0:00:35.82,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's first look at its first role: the data repository.
