Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.65,0:00:43.62,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它能整齐地存储所有系数，以方便后续求解
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.65,0:00:43.62,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}it neatly stores all coefficients for convenient solving.
