Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.35,0:00:55.67,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have a long matrix like this.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.90,0:00:58.42,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每个列向量都代表一个坐标点
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.90,0:00:58.42,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Each column vector represents a coordinate point.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.77,0:01:01.42,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们能把这些列向量都画出来
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.77,0:01:01.42,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we can visualize these column vectors,
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.62,0:01:04.55,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就能解码出这个矩阵所存储的信息
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.62,0:01:04.55,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}we can decode the information stored in the matrix.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.87,0:01:07.40,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们用一个点表示一个坐标
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.87,0:01:07.40,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We use a point to represent each coordinate.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:19.32,0:01:22.45,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然，只要这个矩阵足够长
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.32,0:01:22.45,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Of course, as long as the matrix is long enough,
