Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.52,0:04:12.67,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We can consider the current 3D space as a plane.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.97,0:04:17.70,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}将垂直于这个平面的方向看作第四维度w
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.97,0:04:17.70,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Treat the direction perpendicular to this plane as the fourth dimension, w.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.87,0:04:24.12,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}此时，就可以画出第四个向量
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.87,0:04:24.12,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, we can draw the fourth vector.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.55,0:04:29.12,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们下一步是把它们四个加起来，得到他们四个的线性组合
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.55,0:04:29.12,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The next step is to add these four vectors to obtain their linear combination.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.35,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们需要先退回到三维世界
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.35,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We first step back into the 3D world.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.95,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先将前三个向量加起来
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.95,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Add the first three vectors.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.57,0:04:44.22,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再来到四维世界，将第四个向量加进来
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.57,0:04:44.22,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then move into the 4D world and add the fourth vector.
