Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.50,0:04:48.97,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, the white arrow represents the linear combination of these four vectors.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.72,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}同样，我们调整每个向量前的系数
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.72,Default-L2,atg6,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Similarly, by adjusting the coefficients of each vector,
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.90,0:04:57.97,123,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个代表线性组合的白色向量，就可以构建出整个四维空间
